<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Правила сервера GameHouse</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c0c0c 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Анимированные частицы на фоне */
        .particles {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .particle {
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 15s infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.8);
        }

        .particle:nth-child(1) { left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s; animation-duration: 12s; }
        .particle:nth-child(2) { left: 20%; animation-delay: 2s; animation-duration: 14s; }
        .particle:nth-child(3) { left: 30%; animation-delay: 4s; animation-duration: 11s; }
        .particle:nth-child(4) { left: 40%; animation-delay: 1s; animation-duration: 16s; }
        .particle:nth-child(5) { left: 50%; animation-delay: 3s; animation-duration: 13s; }
        .particle:nth-child(6) { left: 60%; animation-delay: 5s; animation-duration: 15s; }
        .particle:nth-child(7) { left: 70%; animation-delay: 0.5s; animation-duration: 12s; }
        .particle:nth-child(8) { left: 80%; animation-delay: 2.5s; animation-duration: 14s; }
        .particle:nth-child(9) { left: 90%; animation-delay: 4.5s; animation-duration: 11s; }
        .particle:nth-child(10) { left: 15%; animation-delay: 1.5s; animation-duration: 17s; }
        .particle:nth-child(11) { left: 25%; animation-delay: 3.5s; animation-duration: 13s; }
        .particle:nth-child(12) { left: 35%; animation-delay: 0.8s; animation-duration: 15s; }
        .particle:nth-child(13) { left: 45%; animation-delay: 2.8s; animation-duration: 12s; }
        .particle:nth-child(14) { left: 55%; animation-delay: 4.8s; animation-duration: 14s; }
        .particle:nth-child(15) { left: 65%; animation-delay: 1.8s; animation-duration: 16s; }
        .particle:nth-child(16) { left: 75%; animation-delay: 3.8s; animation-duration: 11s; }
        .particle:nth-child(17) { left: 85%; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-duration: 13s; }
        .particle:nth-child(18) { left: 95%; animation-delay: 2.3s; animation-duration: 15s; }
        .particle:nth-child(19) { left: 5%; animation-delay: 4.3s; animation-duration: 12s; }
        .particle:nth-child(20) { left: 50%; animation-delay: 1.3s; animation-duration: 14s; }

        @keyframes float {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            10% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            90% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-100vh) rotate(720deg);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        /* Движущиеся линии на фоне */
        .bg-lines {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .bg-line {
            position: absolute;
            width: 2px;
            height: 100px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.5), transparent);
            animation: lineFall 8s linear infinite;
        }

        .bg-line:nth-child(1) { left: 5%; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(2) { left: 15%; animation-delay: 1s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(3) { left: 25%; animation-delay: 2s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(4) { left: 35%; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(5) { left: 45%; animation-delay: 1.5s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(6) { left: 55%; animation-delay: 2.5s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(7) { left: 65%; animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(8) { left: 75%; animation-delay: 1.8s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(9) { left: 85%; animation-delay: 2.8s; }
        .bg-line:nth-child(10) { left: 95%; animation-delay: 0.3s; }

        @keyframes lineFall {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-100px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(100vh);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(20, 20, 35, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 
                0 25px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5),
                0 0 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1),
                inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            animation: containerAppear 1s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes containerAppear {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(50px) scale(0.95);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
            }
        }

        /* Светящаяся рамка контейнера */
        .container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            right: -2px;
            bottom: -2px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #667eea, #764ba2, #667eea, #764ba2);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 22px;
            animation: glowBorder 3s ease infinite;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        @keyframes glowBorder {
            0%, 100% {
                background-position: 0% 50%;
            }
            50% {
                background-position: 100% 50%;
            }
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3) 0%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.3) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: headerShine 5s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes headerShine {
            0% {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.8);
            position: relative;
            animation: titlePulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        @keyframes titlePulse {
            0%, 100% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.8);
            }
            50% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 50px rgba(102, 126, 234, 1), 0 0 80px rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.8);
            }
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.8;
            position: relative;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 0.8;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .rule {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(40, 40, 60, 0.8) 0%, rgba(30, 30, 50, 0.8) 100%);
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            animation: ruleAppear 0.6s ease-out forwards;
        }

        .rule:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .rule:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .rule:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .rule:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .rule:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .rule:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }
        .rule:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        .rule:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.45s; }
        .rule:nth-child(9) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        .rule:nth-child(10) { animation-delay: 0.55s; }
        .rule:nth-child(11) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
        .rule:nth-child(12) { animation-delay: 0.65s; }
        .rule:nth-child(13) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
        .rule:nth-child(14) { animation-delay: 0.75s; }
        .rule:nth-child(15) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        .rule:nth-child(16) { animation-delay: 0.85s; }

        @keyframes ruleAppear {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .rule::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
            transition: left 0.5s;
        }

        .rule:hover::before {
            left: 100%;
        }

        .rule:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px) scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 
                0 10px 40px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3),
                0 0 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            border-left-color: #a855f7;
        }

        .rule-number {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a78bfa;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .rule-number::before {
            content: '';
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background: #667eea;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: dotPulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes dotPulse {
            0%, 100% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.7);
            }
            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0);
            }
        }

        .rule-text {
            color: #e2e8f0;
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }

        .punishment {
            color: #f87171;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.5);
            animation: punishmentGlow 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes punishmentGlow {
            0%, 100% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.5);
            }
            50% {
                text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.8);
            }
        }

        .warning {
            border-left-color: #fbbf24;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(60, 50, 30, 0.8) 0%, rgba(40, 35, 25, 0.8) 100%);
        }

        .warning .rule-number::before {
            background: #fbbf24;
        }

        .warning:hover {
            border-left-color: #f59e0b;
            box-shadow: 
                0 10px 40px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3),
                0 0 20px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);
        }

        .critical {
            border-left-color: #ef4444;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(60, 30, 30, 0.8) 0%, rgba(40, 25, 25, 0.8) 100%);
        }

        .critical .rule-number::before {
            background: #ef4444;
            animation: criticalPulse 0.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes criticalPulse {
            0%, 100% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7);
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0);
                transform: scale(1.2);
            }
        }

        .critical:hover {
            border-left-color: #dc2626;
            box-shadow: 
                0 10px 40px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3),
                0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        }

        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 30, 45, 0.9) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 35, 0.9) 100%);
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .footer::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #667eea, transparent);
            animation: footerLine 3s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes footerLine {
            0% {
                left: -100%;
            }
            100% {
                left: 100%;
            }
        }

        .footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        .footer p:first-child {
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-weight: bold;
            animation: warningPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes warningPulse {
            0%, 100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 0.7;
            }
        }

        /* Скроллбар стилизация */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 10px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #1a1a2e;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #764ba2, #667eea);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .rule {
                padding: 18px;
            }

            .rule:hover {
                transform: translateX(5px) scale(1.01);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="particles">
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
        <div class="particle"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-lines">
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
        <div class="bg-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>GameHouse Server</h1>
            <p>Правила сервера - обязательны к прочтению</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.0</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Читы — <span class="punishment">бан 50 дней</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.1</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Хранение читов — <span class="punishment">бан 15 дней</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.2</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Спам одного и того же текста в 19+ сообщений — <span class="punishment">мут 1 час</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule warning">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.3</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Злоупотребление дюпами — <span class="punishment">бан 20 дней</span>. Вы можете избежать бана, сообщив о дюпе администрации</div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.4</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Оскорбление администрации — <span class="punishment">мут 1 день</span> (каждый раз будет умножаться на 2)</div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.5</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Спам матами или оскорбление семьи — <span class="punishment">мут 5 часов</span> (также умножается на 2)</div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.6</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Злоупотребление багами или краш сервера — <span class="punishment">бан 10 дней</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule warning">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.7</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Подозрение в читах — временный мут пока вас не проверят (может достигать от 1 дня до месяца)</div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.8</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Багом получить креатив и выдавать себе предметы — <span class="punishment">IP бан 99+ дней</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 1.9</div>
                <div class="rule-text">На турнирах не слушать админов и игнорировать — <span class="punishment">бан 9 часов</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.0</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Спам рекламы — <span class="punishment">мут навсегда + бан 1 день</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.1</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Рекламирование или запуск ботов для рекламы — <span class="punishment">IP бан навсегда</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule warning">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.2</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Если вы стали модератором или админом, когда вам не давали — сообщите администрации или <span class="punishment">IP бан 19 дней</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.3</div>
                <div class="rule-text">При обновлении: взлом администрации — <span class="punishment">IP бан навсегда</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.4</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Не злоупотреблять матами и оскорблениями — <span class="punishment">мут 5 часов</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="rule critical">
                <div class="rule-number">Правило 2.5</div>
                <div class="rule-text">Если вы смогли сломать экономику сервера багом — <span class="punishment">IP бан 10 дней</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Незнание правил не освобождает от ответственности</p>
            <p>Приятной игры на GameHouse Server</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
